text: Anton Kosmač (born 14 December 1976) is a Slovenian long distance runner who specialises in the marathon. He competed in the men's marathon event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male long-distance runners Category:Slovenian male marathon runners Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Slovenia
